  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHAT IS A LIMINAL SPACE?:</strong></h2><br>Liminal spaces are those strange, evocative, and occasionally unsettling locations that appear to be the entrance to another realm. When someone enters a space that is outside of typical space and time, they are said to be in a condition of liminality. These people straddle the boundaries set by law, custom, and convention for the typical roles, behaviors, and positions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TRUE DREAMLIKE EXPERIENCE:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore liminal spaces: Pools, School, Hotel, Parking lot, Office and more.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110510/extras/007bafe11cb81bd971a09d6a93d43d96.poster.avif?t=1692178414\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110510/extras/007bafe11cb81bd971a09d6a93d43d96.webm?t=1692178414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110510/extras/007bafe11cb81bd971a09d6a93d43d96.mp4?t=1692178414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fly through real-time generated clouds.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110510/extras/2497d6f792c03407585ec18ac278658f.poster.avif?t=1692178414\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110510/extras/2497d6f792c03407585ec18ac278658f.webm?t=1692178414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110510/extras/2497d6f792c03407585ec18ac278658f.mp4?t=1692178414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Outrun other vehicles while driving into the sunset.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110510/extras/977c84d9c382d819e68c8dc148f95941.poster.avif?t=1692178414\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110510/extras/977c84d9c382d819e68c8dc148f95941.webm?t=1692178414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110510/extras/977c84d9c382d819e68c8dc148f95941.mp4?t=1692178414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solve puzzles to advance.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CUSTOM ENTITY MODE:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Import your own custom entity and try to escape the backrooms.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110510/extras/8f0c7ff36435777bac1df1bda84f144c.poster.avif?t=1692178414\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110510/extras/8f0c7ff36435777bac1df1bda84f144c.webm?t=1692178414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110510/extras/8f0c7ff36435777bac1df1bda84f144c.mp4?t=1692178414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Importing your own entity has never been easier. Import any picture and sound with just a few clicks.<br><br><strong>Features in this game mode:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Import any picture.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Import any sound.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Modify volume of imported sound.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Modify Player or Entity walk/run speed.</li></ul>",
